  <source>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a clinical trial in patients with Type 2 Diabetes to test the safety of MK0767. This
      study will also see how effective MK0767 is in lowering markers of glucose metabolism and
      improving the lipid profile and non-HDL cholesterol when compared with placebo and
      pioglitazone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
